request.description:
Check the health status of the ScanMyFood Backend service.

**Response:**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "status": "UP",
    "service": "Food Scan AI Backend"
  }
}
```

Analyze product images (front and nutrition label) using AI to extract nutritional information.

**Request:**
- Content-Type: multipart/form-data
- frontImage: Product front image file
- labelImage: Nutrition label image file

**Response:**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "product": {
      "name": "string",
      "category": "string"
    },
    "nutritionAnalysis": {
      "totalQuantity": { "value": 0, "unit": "string" },
      "servingSize": { "value": 0, "unit": "string" },
      "nutrients": [...],
      "primaryConcerns": [...]
    }
  }
}
```

body.raw:
{
    "description": "A bowl of rice with grilled chicken and vegetables"
}

request.description:
Analyze a text description of food using AI to estimate nutritional content.

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "description": "string - description of the food/meal"
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "mealName": "string",
    "analyzedFoodItems": [...],
    "totalPlateNutrients": [...]
  }
}
```

body.raw:
{
    "description": "A bowl of pasta with tomato sauce and fresh basil"
}

request.description:
Check if a user is new (not yet registered in the system).

**Path Parameters:**
- firebaseUid: Firebase User ID

**Response:**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "isNewUser": true | false
  }
}
```

Create a new user or find existing user by Firebase UID.

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "firebaseUid": "string",
  "email": "string",
  "displayName": "string"
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "userId": "string",
    "created": true
  }
}
```

Complete user onboarding with preferences and health metrics.

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "firebaseUid": "string",
  "preferences": {
    "dietaryPreference": "string",
    "country": "string"
  },
  "healthMetrics": {
    "heightFeet": number,
    "heightInches": number,
    "weightKg": number,
    "goal": "string"
  }
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "success": true,
    "message": "Onboarding completed successfully"
  }
}
```

Check if a user has completed the onboarding process.

**Path Parameters:**
- firebaseUid: Firebase User ID

**Response:**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "isOnboardingComplete": true | false
  }
}
```

Save or update user dietary preferences.

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "firebaseUid": "string",
  "dietaryPreference": "string",
  "country": "string"
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "success": true,
    "message": "Preferences saved successfully"
  }
}
```

Save a scanned product label with its analysis to the user's intake history.

**Request:**
- Content-Type: multipart/form-data
- foodImage: Image file of the product
- saveScannedLabelInput: JSON object with userId and productAnalysisResponse

**saveScannedLabelInput structure:**
```json
{
  "userId": "string",
  "productAnalysisResponse": {
    "product": {
      "name": "string",
      "category": "string"
    },
    "nutritionAnalysis": {
      "totalQuantity": {...},
      "servingSize": {...},
      "nutrients": [...],
      "primaryConcerns": [...]
    }
  }
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Scanned food intake saved successfully."
}
```
